  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase 1 multi-center study designed to determine the maximum tolerated dose (MTD)
      and toxicity of intratumoral administration of VSV-IFNβ-NIS in patients with refractory
      advanced/metastatic solid tumors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
